      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STRAPPING PROPHET (1) has been runner-up at his past four starts but looks to get a few things in his favour today that can see him go one better. A better draw today can see him sit closer than he did last time out. Can finally go one better and turn the tables on FLAMING RONDA (4) who edged out STRAPPING PROPHET last time at Pinjarra. The inside draw should see her get every chance in the run and CJP now hops on board. Can bring up the hat-trick. GOD'S GRIN (8) was strong first-up and ran to a similar level last start at this track when the race favourite. Nottle rides now and out to 1600m for the first time looks a good move. Can sit handy today and with improvement on the cards, she makes plenty of appeal. HOPE TO RULE (6) is racing in top order and has to be included on her recent form. MOHEGAN RULER (3) can sit much closer today than he has done so far this campaign and another forward showing is expected.",
